comments.body:
It could look like this:

```php
$run = $workflowClient->start($stub, 'Hello World!');

/** @var WorkflowExecutionStatus $status */
$status = $run->describe()->info->status;
```

```php
enum WorkflowExecutionStatus: int
{
    case Unspecified = 0;
    case Running = 1;
    case Completed = 2;
    case Failed = 3;
    case Canceled = 4;
    case Terminated = 5;
    case ContinuedAsNew = 6;
    case TimedOut = 7;
}
```
